{
  "taskId": "task_1778145772393_669",
  "requestedModel": "anti-gemini-3.1-pro-high",
  "text": "리팩토링 작업을 시작하겠습니다. DEV_ADVISOR 님의 피드백에 따라 컴포넌트 분리, API 연동 준비, 하드코딩 제거를 중심으로 코드를 개선하겠습니다.\n\n### 1. `index.html` (루트 파일)\n기존 HTML 구조를 유지하되, 단일 스크립트 대신 모듈화된 React 애플리케이션을 로드하도록 수정합니다.\n\n```html\n<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"ko\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\" />\n    <title>MyCrew Timeline View (Refactored)</title>\n    <script src=\"https://unpkg.com/react@18/umd/react.development.js\"></script>\n    <script src=\"https://unpkg.com/react-dom@18/umd/react-dom.development.js\"></script>\n    <script src=\"https://unpkg.com/@babel/standalone/babel.min.js\"></script>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"src/style.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div id=\"root\"></div>\n    <script type=\"text/babel\" data-type=\"module\" src=\"src/main.jsx\"></script>\n</body>\n</html>\n```\n\n### 2. `src/style.css` (스타일시트 분리)\n인라인으로 존재하던 CSS를 별도 파일로 분리하여 관리합니다.\n\n```css\n:root {\n    --bg-color: #1a1a1a;\n    --text-color: #e0e0e0;\n    --border-color: #333;\n    --input-bg: #2a2a2a;\n    --system-color: #888;\n    --thought-color: #5a9;\n    --result-color: #7c5;\n    --user-color: #58c;\n    --sender-bg: #333;\n    --code-bg: #222;\n    --font-family-sans: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Segoe UI\", Roboto,\n        Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, \"Apple Color Emoji\", \"Segoe UI Emoji\";\n    --font-family-mono: \"SF Mono\", \"Fira Code\", \"Fira Mono\", \"Roboto Mono\",\n        monospace;\n}\n\nbody {\n    background-color: var(--bg-color);\n    color: var(--text-color);\n    font-family: var(--font-family-sans);\n    margin: 0;\n    display: flex;\n    justify-content: center;\n    align-items: center;\n    height: 100vh;\n}\n\n.timeline-container {\n    width: 100%;\n    max-width: 800px;\n    height: 90vh;\n    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);\n    border-radius: 8px;\n    display: flex;\n    flex-direction: column;\n    overflow: hidden;\n    background-color: #202124;\n}\n\n.timeline {\n    flex-grow: 1;\n    overflow-y: auto;\n    padding: 20px;\n    display: flex;\n    flex-direction: column;\n    gap: 20px;\n}\n\n.message {\n    display: flex;\n    gap: 12px;\n    align-items: flex-start;\n}\n\n.avatar {\n    width: 32px;\n    height: 32px;\n    border-radius: 50%;\n    background-color: var(--sender-bg);\n    display: flex;\n    justify-content: center;\n    align-items: center;\n    font-weight: bold;\n    font-size: 14px;\n    flex-shrink: 0;\n}\n\n.content {\n    padding-top: 4px;\n    max-width: calc(100% - 44px);\n}\n\n.sender {\n    font-weight: bold;\n    margin-bottom: 4px;\n    font-size: 14px;\n}\n\n.text {\n    line-height: 1.6;\n    white-space: pre-wrap;\n    word-wrap: break-word;\n}\n\n.message.system .text { color: var(--system-color); font-style: italic; }\n.message.thought .text { color: var(--thought-color); }\n.message.result .text { color: var(--result-color); }\n.message.user .sender { color: var(--user-color); }\n\npre {\n    background-color: var(--code-bg);\n    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);\n    border-radius: 4px;\n    padding: 12px;\n    overflow-x: auto;\n    font-family: var(--font-family-mono);\n    font-size: 14px;\n}\n\ncode {\n    font-family: var(--font-family-mono);\n}\n\n.message-input-form {\n    display: flex;\n    padding: 12px;\n    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);\n    gap: 10px;\n}\n\n.message-input {\n    flex-grow: 1;\n    background-color: var(--input-bg);\n    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);\n    border-radius: 6px;\n    color: var(--text-color);\n    padding: 10px 14px;\n    font-size: 16px;\n    resize: none;\n}\n\n.message-input:focus {\n    outline: none;\n    border-color: var(--user-color);\n}\n\n.send-button {\n    background-color: var(--user-color);\n    color: white;\n    border: none;\n    border-radius: 6px;\n    padding: 0 20px;\n    font-size: 16px;\n    cursor: pointer;\n    transition: background-color 0.2s;\n}\n\n.send-button:hover {\n    background-color: #69d;\n}\n```\n\n### 3. `src/api/messages.js` (API 모듈)\n데이터를 제공하는 부분을 별도 파일로 분리하여 향후 실제 API로 교체하기 용이하게 만듭니다.\n\n```javascript\nconst mockData = [\n    { id: 1, type: 'system', sender: 'System', text: 'Task started: 타임라인 뷰 UI 프론트엔드 구현' },\n    { id: 2, type: 'thought', sender: 'PICO', text: '요구사항 분석: 실시간 로그, AI 사고 과정, 결과물을 타임라인 형태로 보여줘야 함. React와 단일 HTML 파일로 빠르게 프로토타이핑하는 것이 좋겠군. 메시지 타입(system, thought, result, user)에 따라 다른 스타일을 적용해야겠다.' },\n    { id: 3, type: 'result', sender: 'PICO', text: '기본 HTML 구조와 CSS 스타일을 완성했습니다. 이제 React 컴포넌트를 작성하여 동적으로 메시지를 렌더링하겠습니다.' },\n    { id: 4, type: 'result', sender: 'PICO', text: `\\`\\`\\`html\n<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n    <title>Timeline View</title>\n    <script src=\"https://unpkg.com/react@18/umd/react.development.js\"></script>\n    <script src=\"https://unpkg.com/react-dom@18/umd/react-dom.development.js\"></script>\n    <script src=\"https://unpkg.com/@babel/standalone/babel.min.js\"></script>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div id=\"root\"></div>\n</body>\n</html>\n\\`\\`\\`` },\n    { id: 5, type: 'user', sender: 'Alex', text: 'PICO, 진행 상황 공유해주세요.' },\n];\n\n// API 호출을 시뮬레이션하는 비동기 함수\nexport const fetchMessages = async () => {\n    console.log(\"Fetching messages...\");\n    // 네트워크 지연 시뮬레이션\n    await new Promise(resolve => setTimeout(resolve, 500));\n    console.log(\"Messages fetched.\");\n    return mockData;\n};\n\n// 새 메시지 전송을 시뮬레이션하는 함수\nexport const postMessage = async (message) => {\n    console.log(\"Posting new message:\", message);\n    await new Promise(resolve => setTimeout(resolve, 200));\n    // 실제 API라면 여기서 서버에 데이터를 전송하고 응답을 받음\n    return { ...message, id: Date.now() };\n};\n```\n\n### 4. `src/hooks/useMessages.js` (커스텀 훅)\n메시지 상태 관리 및 데이터 페칭 로직을 컴포넌트로부터 분리합니다. `@tanstack/react-query` 도입 시 이 파일을 수정하면 됩니다.\n\n```javascript\nimport { fetchMessages, postMessage } from '../api/messages.js';\n\nconst { useState, useEffect, useCallback } = React;\n\nexport const useMessages = () => {\n    const [messages, setMessages] = useState([]);\n    const [loading, setLoading] = useState(true);\n\n    useEffect(() => {\n        const loadMessages = async () => {\n            try {\n                const initialMessages = await fetchMessages();\n                setMessages(initialMessages);\n            } catch (error) {\n                console.error(\"Failed to fetch messages:\", error);\n            } finally {\n                setLoading(false);\n            }\n        };\n        loadMessages();\n    }, []);\n\n    const addMessage = useCallback(async (newMessage) => {\n        // Optimistic UI Update\n        const tempId = `temp-${Date.now()}`;\n        const messageWithTempId = { ...newMessage, id: tempId };\n        setMessages(prevMessages => [...prevMessages, messageWithTempId]);\n\n        try {\n            const savedMessage = await postMessage(newMessage);\n            setMessages(prevMessages => \n                prevMessages.map(msg => \n                    msg.id === tempId ? savedMessage : msg\n                )\n            );\n        } catch (error) {\n            console.error(\"Failed to post message:\", error);\n            // Rollback on error\n            setMessages(prevMessages => prevMessages.filter(msg => msg.id !== tempId));\n        }\n    }, []);\n\n    return { messages, loading, addMessage };\n};\n```\n\n### 5. `src/components/Message.jsx`\n개별 메시지를 렌더링하는 재사용 가능한 컴포넌트입니다.\n\n```javascript\nconst Message = ({ message }) => {\n    const { type, sender, text } = message;\n\n    const renderText = (rawText) => {\n        const codeBlockRegex = /```(\\w*)\\n([\\s\\S]*?)```/g;\n        const parts = [];\n        let lastIndex = 0;\n        let match;\n\n        while ((match = codeBlockRegex.exec(rawText)) !== null) {\n            if (match.index > lastIndex) {\n                parts.push(rawText.substring(lastIndex, match.index));\n            }\n            const codeContent = match[2];\n            parts.push(\n                <pre key={match.index}>\n                    <code>{codeContent}</code>\n                </pre>\n            );\n            lastIndex = codeBlockRegex.lastIndex;\n        }\n\n        if (lastIndex < rawText.length) {\n            parts.push(rawText.substring(lastIndex));\n        }\n\n        return parts.map((part, index) => <React.Fragment key={index}>{part}</React.Fragment>);\n    };\n\n    return (\n        <div className={`message ${type}`}>\n            <div className=\"avatar\">{sender.slice(0, 2).toUpperCase()}</div>\n            <div className=\"content\">\n                <div className=\"sender\">{sender}</div>\n                <div className=\"text\">{renderText(text)}</div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    );\n};\n\nexport default Message;\n```\n\n### 6. `src/components/Timeline.jsx`\n메시지 목록 전체를 감싸고 스크롤 로직을 처리하는 컴포넌트입니다.\n\n```javascript\nimport Message from './Message.jsx';\n\nconst { useEffect, useRef } = React;\n\nconst Timeline = ({ messages, loading }) => {\n    const timelineEndRef = useRef(null);\n\n    const scrollToBottom = () => {\n        timelineEndRef.current?.scrollIntoView({ behavior: \"smooth\" });\n    };\n\n    useEffect(() => {\n        scrollToBottom();\n    }, [messages]);\n\n    if (loading) {\n        return <div className=\"timeline\">Loading messages...</div>;\n    }\n\n    return (\n        <div className=\"timeline\">\n            {messages.map(msg => (\n                <Message key={msg.id} message={msg} />\n            ))}\n            <div ref={timelineEndRef} />\n        </div>\n    );\n};\n\nexport default Timeline;\n```\n\n### 7. `src/components/MessageInput.jsx`\n메시지 입력을 담당하는 컴포넌트입니다. 하드코딩된 'PICO' 대신 `currentUser` prop을 사용합니다.\n\n```javascript\nconst { useState } = React;\n\nconst MessageInput = ({ onSendMessage, currentUser }) => {\n    const [text, setText] = useState('');\n\n    const handleSubmit = (e) => {\n        e.preventDefault();\n        if (text.trim()) {\n            const newMessage = {\n                type: 'user',\n                sender: currentUser.name,\n                text: text.trim(),\n            };\n            onSendMessage(newMessage);\n            setText('');\n        }\n    };\n\n    return (\n        <form className=\"message-input-form\" onSubmit={handleSubmit}>\n            <textarea\n                className=\"message-input\"\n                value={text}\n                onChange={(e) => setText(e.target.value)}\n                placeholder=\"메시지를 입력하세요...\"\n                rows=\"1\"\n            />\n            <button type=\"submit\" className=\"send-button\">Send</button>\n        </form>\n    );\n};\n\nexport default MessageInput;\n```\n\n### 8. `src/App.jsx` (애플리케이션 루트 컴포넌트)\n분리된 컴포넌트들을 조립하고, 상태와 로직을 `useMessages` 훅에서 가져와 주입합니다.\n\n```javascript\nimport Timeline from './components/Timeline.jsx';\nimport MessageInput from './components/MessageInput.jsx';\nimport { useMessages } from './hooks/useMessages.js';\n\nconst App = () => {\n    const { messages, loading, addMessage } = useMessages();\n    \n    // 현재 로그인된 사용자를 시뮬레이션. \n    // 추후 Context API나 인증 라이브러리에서 가져올 값.\n    const currentUser = { name: 'Alex' };\n\n    return (\n        <div className=\"timeline-container\">\n            <Timeline messages={messages} loading={loading} />\n            <MessageInput onSendMessage={addMessage} currentUser={currentUser} />\n        </div>\n    );\n};\n\nexport default App;\n```\n\n### 9. `src/main.jsx` (React 진입점)\n`App` 컴포넌트를 DOM에 렌더링합니다.\n\n```javascript\nimport App from './App.jsx';\n\nconst container = document.getElementById('root');\nconst root = ReactDOM.createRoot(container);\nroot.render(<App />);\n```\n\n<file_operations>\n[\n  {\n    \"action\": \"write\",\n    \"type\": \"output\",\n    \"path\": \"index.html\",\n    \"content\": \"<!DOCTYPE html>\\n<html lang=\\\"ko\\\">\\n<head>\\n    <meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\" />\\n    <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\\\" />\\n    <title>MyCrew Timeline View (Refactored)</title>\\n    <script src=\\\"https://unpkg.com/react@18/umd/react.development.js\\\"></script>\\n    <script src=\\\"https://unpkg.com/react-dom@18/umd/react-dom.development.js\\\"></script>\\n    <script src=\\\"https://unpkg.com/@babel/standalone/babel.min.js\\\"></script>\\n    <link rel=\\\"stylesheet\\\" href=\\\"src/style.css\\\">\\n</head>\\n<body>\\n    <div id=\\\"root\\\"></div>\\n    <script type=\\\"text/babel\\\" data-type=\\\"module\\\" src=\\\"src/main.jsx\\\"></script>\\n</body>\\n</html>\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"action\": \"write\",\n    \"type\": \"output\",\n    \"path\": \"src/style.css\",\n    \"content\": \":root {\\n    --bg-color: #1a1a1a;\\n    --text-color: #e0e0e0;\\n    --border-color: #333;\\n    --input-bg: #2a2a2a;\\n    --system-color: #888;\\n    --thought-color: #5a9;\\n    --result-color: #7c5;\\n    --user-color: #58c;\\n    --sender-bg: #333;\\n    --code-bg: #222;\\n    --font-family-sans: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \\\"Segoe UI\\\", Roboto,\\n        Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, \\\"Apple Color Emoji\\\", \\\"Segoe UI Emoji\\\";\\n    --font-family-mono: \\\"SF Mono\\\", \\\"Fira Code\\\", \\\"Fira Mono\\\", \\\"Roboto Mono\\\",\\n        monospace;\\n}\\n\\nbody {\\n    background-color: var(--bg-color);\\n    color: var(--text-color);\\n    font-family: var(--font-family-sans);\\n    margin: 0;\\n    display: flex;\\n    justify-content: center;\\n    align-items: center;\\n    height: 100vh;\\n}\\n\\n.timeline-container {\\n    width: 100%;\\n    max-width: 800px;\\n    height: 90vh;\\n    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);\\n    border-radius: 8px;\\n    display: flex;\\n    flex-direction: column;\\n    overflow: hidden;\\n    background-color: #202124;\\n}\\n\\n.timeline {\\n    flex-grow: 1;\\n    overflow-y: auto;\\n    padding: 20px;\\n    display: flex;\\n    flex-direction: column;\\n    gap: 20px;\\n}\\n\\n.message {\\n    display: flex;\\n    gap: 12px;\\n    align-items: flex-start;\\n}\\n\\n.avatar {\\n    width: 32px;\\n    height: 32px;\\n    border-radius: 50%;\\n    background-color: var(--sender-bg);\\n    display: flex;\\n    justify-content: center;\\n    align-items: center;\\n    font-weight: bold;\\n    font-size: 14px;\\n    flex-shrink: 0;\\n}\\n\\n.content {\\n    padding-top: 4px;\\n    max-width: calc(100% - 44px);\\n}\\n\\n.sender {\\n    font-weight: bold;\\n    margin-bottom: 4px;\\n    font-size: 14px;\\n}\\n\\n.text {\\n    line-height: 1.6;\\n    white-space: pre-wrap;\\n    word-wrap: break-word;\\n}\\n\\n.message.system .text { color: var(--system-color); font-style: italic; }\\n.message.thought .text { color: var(--thought-color); }\\n.message.result .text { color: var(--result-color); }\\n.message.user .sender { color: var(--user-color); }\\n\\npre {\\n    background-color: var(--code-bg);\\n    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);\\n    border-radius: 4px;\\n    padding: 12px;\\n    overflow-x: auto;\\n    font-family: var(--font-family-mono);\\n    font-size: 14px;\\n}\\n\\ncode {\\n    font-family: var(--font-family-mono);\\n}\\n\\n.message-input-form {\\n    display: flex;\\n    padding: 12px;\\n    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);\\n    gap: 10px;\\n}\\n\\n.message-input {\\n    flex-grow: 1;\\n    background-color: var(--input-bg);\\n    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);\\n    border-radius: 6px;\\n    color: var(--text-color);\\n    padding: 10px 14px;\\n    font-size: 16px;\\n    resize: none;\\n}\\n\\n.message-input:focus {\\n    outline: none;\\n    border-color: var(--user-color);\\n}\\n\\n.send-button {\\n    background-color: var(--user-color);\\n    color: white;\\n    border: none;\\n    border-radius: 6px;\\n    padding: 0 20px;\\n    font-size: 16px;\\n    cursor: pointer;\\n    transition: background-color 0.2s;\\n}\\n\\n.send-button:hover {\\n    background-color: #69d;\\n}\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"action\": \"write\",\n    \"type\": \"output\",\n    \"path\": \"src/api/messages.js\",\n    \"content\": \"const mockData = [\\n    { id: 1, type: 'system', sender: 'System', text: 'Task started: 타임라인 뷰 UI 프론트엔드 구현' },\\n    { id: 2, type: 'thought', sender: 'PICO', text: '요구사항 분석: 실시간 로그, AI 사고 과정, 결과물을 타임라인 형태로 보여줘야 함. React와 단일 HTML 파일로 빠르게 프로토타이핑하는 것이 좋겠군. 메시지 타입(system, thought, result, user)에 따라 다른 스타일을 적용해야겠다.' },\\n    { id: 3, type: 'result', sender: 'PICO', text: '기본 HTML 구조와 CSS 스타일을 완성했습니다. 이제 React 컴포넌트를 작성하여 동적으로 메시지를 렌더링하겠습니다.' },\\n    { id: 4, type: 'result', sender: 'PICO', text: ````html\\\\n<!DOCTYPE html>\\\\n<html>\\\\n<head>\\\\n    <title>Timeline View</title>\\\\n    <script src=\\\"https://unpkg.com/react@18/umd/react.development.js\\\"></script>\\\\n    <script src=\\\"https://unpkg.com/react-dom@18/umd/react-dom.development.js\\\"></script>\\\\n    <script src=\\\"https://unpkg.com/@babel/standalone/babel.min.js\\\"></script>\\\\n</head>\\\\n<body>\\\\n    <div id=\\\"root\\\"></div>\\\\n</body>\\\\n</html>\\\\n```` },\\n    { id: 5, type: 'user', sender: 'Alex', text: 'PICO, 진행 상황 공유해주세요.' },\\n];\\n\\n// API 호출을 시뮬레이션하는 비동기 함수\\nexport const fetchMessages = async () => {\\n    console.log(\\\"Fetching messages...\\\");\\n    // 네트워크 지연 시뮬레이션\\n    await new Promise(resolve => setTimeout(resolve, 500));\\n    console.log(\\\"Messages fetched.\\\");\\n    return mockData;\\n};\\n\\n// 새 메시지 전송을 시뮬레이션하는 함수\\nexport const postMessage = async (message) => {\\n    console.log(\\\"Posting new message:\\\", message);\\n    await new Promise(resolve => setTimeout(resolve, 200));\\n    // 실제 API라면 여기서 서버에 데이터를 전송하고 응답을 받음\\n    return { ...message, id: Date.now() };\\n};\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"action\": \"write\",\n    \"type\": \"output\",\n    \"path\": \"src/hooks/useMessages.js\",\n    \"content\": \"import { fetchMessages, postMessage } from '../api/messages.js';\\n\\nconst { useState, useEffect, useCallback } = React;\\n\\nexport const useMessages = () => {\\n    const [messages, setMessages] = useState([]);\\n    const [loading, setLoading] = useState(true);\\n\\n    useEffect(() => {\\n        const loadMessages = async () => {\\n            try {\\n                const initialMessages = await fetchMessages();\\n                setMessages(initialMessages);\\n            } catch (error) {\\n                console.error(\\\"Failed to fetch messages:\\\", error);\\n            } finally {\\n                setLoading(false);\\n            }\\n        };\\n        loadMessages();\\n    }, []);\\n\\n    const addMessage = useCallback(async (newMessage) => {\\n        // Optimistic UI Update\\n        const tempId = `temp-${Date.now()}`;\\n        const messageWithTempId = { ...newMessage, id: tempId };\\n        setMessages(prevMessages => [...prevMessages, messageWithTempId]);\\n\\n        try {\\n            const savedMessage = await postMessage(newMessage);\\n            setMessages(prevMessages => \\n                prevMessages.map(msg => \\n                    msg.id === tempId ? savedMessage : msg\\n                )\\n            );\\n        } catch (error) {\\n            console.error(\\\"Failed to post message:\\\", error);\\n            // Rollback on error\\n            setMessages(prevMessages => prevMessages.filter(msg => msg.id !== tempId));\\n        }\\n    }, []);\\n\\n    return { messages, loading, addMessage };\\n};\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"action\": \"write\",\n    \"type\": \"output\",\n    \"path\": \"src/components/Message.jsx\",\n    \"content\": \"const Message = ({ message }) => {\\n    const { type, sender, text } = message;\\n\\n    const renderText = (rawText) => {\\n        const codeBlockRegex = /```(\\\\w*)\\\\n([\\\\s\\\\S]*?)```/g;\\n        const parts = [];\\n        let lastIndex = 0;\\n        let match;\\n\\n        while ((match = codeBlockRegex.exec(rawText)) !== null) {\\n            if (match.index > lastIndex) {\\n                parts.push(rawText.substring(lastIndex, match.index));\\n            }\\n            const codeContent = match[2];\\n            parts.push(\\n                <pre key={match.index}>\\n                    <code>{codeContent}</code>\\n                </pre>\\n            );\\n            lastIndex = codeBlockRegex.lastIndex;\\n        }\\n\\n        if (lastIndex < rawText.length) {\\n            parts.push(rawText.substring(lastIndex));\\n",
